<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script defer src='/js/index.js'></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/static/pretendard.min.css" />
    <link href='/css/index.css' rel='stylesheet' />
    <title>Movie Insight</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Movie Insight</h1>
        <p>재미있는 영화를 찾고 계신가요?</p>
        <form id='search_form' action="/search">
            <input type="search" name="query" placeholder="검색" />
            <button type="submit">검색</button>
        </form>
    </header>

    <div id='main'>
        <div class='movie_container' id="trending">
            <h2 class="movie_list_title">인기 영화</h2>

            <ul class="movie_list">

            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class='movie_container' id="now_playing">
            <h2 class="movie_list_title">최신 영화</h2>

            <ul class="movie_list">
                
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>